dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Washington County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2020. The following features are included: 'WASHINGTON_HYDRO_POLY_2020' and 'WASHINGTON_HYDRO_LINE_2020'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.washcowisco.gov/portal/apps/sites/#/maps
